sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as Browser<br/>(Data Scientist)
    participant Gateway as Gateway API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAuth as Kubernetes API<br/>(Auth Check)
    participant Fastify as Fastify Backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant GenAI as Gen AI BFF<br/>8143/TCP HTTPS
    participant MaaS as MaaS BFF<br/>8243/TCP HTTPS
    participant LlamaStack as LlamaStack API<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.3
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 1: User Request to Dashboard UI

    Browser->>Gateway: GET / (HTTPS/443)<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>KRBP: Forward (HTTPS/8443)<br/>TLS (service cert)
    KRBP->>K8sAuth: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(can user list projects?)
    K8sAuth-->>KRBP: Allowed
    KRBP->>Fastify: Forward (HTTP/8080)<br/>Headers: x-forwarded-access-token,<br/>x-auth-request-user,<br/>x-auth-request-groups
    Fastify-->>KRBP: index.html + React SPA bundle<br/>+ Module Federation config
    KRBP-->>Gateway: Response (HTTPS)
    Gateway-->>Browser: Dashboard UI (HTTPS)

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 2: Module Federation API Call (Gen AI)

    Browser->>Gateway: POST /_mf/gen-ai/api/v1/responses<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
    Gateway->>KRBP: Forward (HTTPS/8443)
    KRBP->>Fastify: Forward with x-forwarded-access-token
    Fastify->>GenAI: Proxy /_mf/gen-ai/*<br/>HTTPS/8143<br/>x-forwarded-access-token passthrough
    GenAI->>K8sAuth: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(can user access service?)
    K8sAuth-->>GenAI: Allowed
    GenAI->>LlamaStack: POST /v1/responses<br/>Bearer Token (forwarded)
    LlamaStack-->>GenAI: AI Response
    GenAI-->>Fastify: JSON Response
    Fastify-->>KRBP: Forward Response
    KRBP-->>Gateway: Response (HTTPS)
    Gateway-->>Browser: AI Response

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 2b: Inter-BFF Token Delegation

    GenAI->>MaaS: POST /api/v1/tokens/bff<br/>HTTPS/8243 (inter-BFF)<br/>User Token passthrough
    MaaS-->>GenAI: Token Response

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 3: Kubernetes Watch Stream

    Browser->>Gateway: WebSocket Upgrade<br/>WSS/443
    Gateway->>KRBP: WSS/8443
    KRBP->>Fastify: WS/8080<br/>Bearer token in subprotocol<br/>(base64url-encoded)
    Fastify->>K8sAPI: WSS/6443<br/>User Token from subprotocol
    K8sAPI-->>Fastify: Watch Events (streaming)
    Fastify-->>KRBP: Forward events
    KRBP-->>Gateway: Forward events
    Gateway-->>Browser: Real-time K8s updates

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 4: K8s API Passthrough

    Browser->>Gateway: GET /api/k8s/apis/serving.kserve.io/v1beta1/inferenceservices<br/>HTTPS/443
    Gateway->>KRBP: Forward
    KRBP->>Fastify: Forward with user token
    Fastify->>K8sAPI: GET /apis/serving.kserve.io/...<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>User Token passthrough
    K8sAPI-->>Fastify: InferenceService list
    Fastify-->>KRBP: JSON Response
    KRBP-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Browser: K8s Resources
